settings.title: What is the canvas made of?
settings.answer: Each canvas is made with choice poly-cotton canvas. Includes Lifetime UV protection to stay vibrant. Solid wood backing.

settings.title: Do you have my song?
settings.answer: Yes! We can do any song. Just let us know what song you want and we can do the rest.

settings.title: How do I order?
settings.answer: Select the size and quantity of canvas and any customizations and we will do the rest! We will send a preview within 3-4 business days to get your approval before production/shipment.

settings.title: What is the best size for me?
settings.answer: Our most popular size is the 24x48''. We do recommend measuring the space where you want the canvas to be hung.

settings.title: What is the turnaound time?
settings.answer: Short answer with standard shipping 5-9 business days. Priority shipping 2-5 business days. The sooner the proof is approve the faster we can get it out.

settings.title: Does the canvas arrive ready to hang?
settings.answer: Yes, it arrives ready to hang with a wooden backing. All you need to do is decide where to hang your new canvas.
